quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  107,1,"Did you see him who gives the lie to the Reward and Punishment of the Hereafter?",footnotes:182856:1|182857:2|182858:3
  107,2,"Such is the one who repulses the orphans away,",footnotes:182859:1|182860:2
  107,3,"and urges not the feeding of the needy.",footnotes:182861:1|182862:2
  107,4,"Woe, then, to those who pray,",footnotes:182863:1
  107,5,"but are heedless in their Prayers,",footnotes:182864:1
  107,6,"those who do good (in order) to be seen,",footnotes:182865:1
  107,7,"and deny people the articles of common necessity.",footnotes:182866:1
